tracks.title: Respighi Circenses Festival
tracks.desc: This piece begins in dramatic fashion with crashing percussion, trumpet fanfare and surging strings.  The orchestra drives forward with intensity before building to an immense conclusion.

tracks.title: Respighi Epiphany Festival
tracks.desc: A dense wave of sound starts the piece as instruments careen around wildly.  After a slight diversion into a carnivalesque figure the piece comes to a dramatic close.

tracks.title: Respighi Prelude
tracks.desc: The piece opens with a stately orchestral figure before quickly fluttering strings and warbling reeds take the lead.

tracks.title: Respighi La Columba
tracks.desc: A yearning melody is traded amongst the instruments as strings flutter in the background.

tracks.title: Respighi La Gallina
tracks.desc: Jumpy strings propel the orchestra as the leaping melody drives forward.

tracks.title: Respighi L Usignuolo
tracks.desc: Soft flutes play a reflective melody as the orchestra offers subtle support.

tracks.title: Respighi Il Cuccu
tracks.desc: Cascading flutes give way to epic and sweeping strings that glide forward with an introspective melody.

tracks.title: Rimsky Korsakov Flight Of The Bumble Bee
tracks.desc: Furiously fluttering strings and woodwinds buzz wildly and drive this piece forward with intensity.

tracks.title: Rossini Barber Of Seville
tracks.desc: Powerful orchestral bursts are countered by sections of softly sweeping strings.

tracks.title: Rossini Largo Al Factotum (from The Barber Of Seville)
tracks.desc: Strings fly around playfully as the orchestra builds.  Powerful vocals drive forward with potency.

tracks.title: Rossini La Cenerentola (Overture)
tracks.desc: Dynamic shifts lend this piece power as softly lilting strings give way to tense and dramatic passages.

tracks.title: Rossini William Tell (Full Overture)
tracks.desc: Elegiac strings begin the piece softly before the orchestra builds with furiously cascading strings.  The entrance of military trumpet begins a wild race towards the piece's conclusion.

tracks.title: Rossini William Tell (Trumpet Entry)
tracks.desc: Epic horns enter and are soon joined by the entire orchestra.  The orchestra builds steadily and crashes with power.

tracks.title: Saint Carnival Of The Animals (Finale)
tracks.desc: Sweeping piano opens the piece before a playful melody emerges.  The piano leaps and dives as the orchestra maintains the atmosphere.

tracks.title: Sarasate Carmen Fantasy
tracks.desc: A dramatic and exotic theme bursts forward.  Passionate violin leads the way with intense harmonic-minor passages.

tracks.title: Sarasate Zapateado
tracks.desc: Quick and playful piano provides support for fleet-fingered violin.

tracks.title: Satie Gymnopodie 1
tracks.desc: Introspective piano plays a reflective melody over sweet major seventh chords.

tracks.title: Schubert Piano Trio in B flat (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Pounding piano and sweeping violin and cello open the piece powerfully.  The dramatic melody is traded amongst the instruments as it works towards an intense conclusion.

tracks.title: Schubert Piano Trio in B flat (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Graceful piano allows for the violin and cello to glide sweetly as a reflective melody emerges.

tracks.title: Schubert Piano Trio in B flat (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: A bouncing rhythm drives this movement forward as the graceful strings soar over the shimmering piano.

tracks.title: Schubert Piano Trio in B flat (4th movement)
tracks.desc: Jaunty violin leads off this movement and the buoyant melody is exchanged between the instruments before the piece closes triumphantly.

tracks.title: Schubert Ave Maria
tracks.desc: Delicate piano opens this piece before yearning vocals enter, ascending to epic emotional heights.

tracks.title: Schubert Gloria (from German Mass)
tracks.desc: The choir sings triumphantly as subtle orchestral accompaniment adds to the joyous atmosphere.

tracks.title: Schubert Kyrie (Opus 45)
tracks.desc: A lush and triumphant choral arrangement gives this piece considerable weight and expressive power.

tracks.title: Schubert Salve Regina (Opus 386)
tracks.desc: A joyous melody is carried aloft through dense choral harmonization.

tracks.title: Accelerating Springtime Dance
tracks.desc: A happy rhythm beats under this flowing piece, as strings and clarinet weave a jazzy and upbeat melody the tempo increases, giving a palpable sense of anticipation. The clarinet swings with a humorous and pleased grace.

tracks.title: Crescendo Romance
tracks.desc: Warm piano and string lines intermingle and sway, gently expanding and swelling with emotion. Equally timmid and swelling with courage the charming melody flows with emotive grace.

tracks.title: Follow The Trail
tracks.desc: A bluesy clarinet weaves an enchanting line as congas and piano work a dark, shadowy rhythm. Piano adds eerie touches as a bassy synth begins to growl. The piece wanders into uncharted areas, the clarinet enters again to bring the piece back home.

tracks.title: From Waterdrops To Ravelish
tracks.desc: A winding, decending melody with twinkling piano, clarinet and strings flows with gentle emotions. An introspective quietude envelopes the piece as it drips like a golden-hued liquid.

tracks.title: Hypnotic Lullaby
tracks.desc: Bells and chimes weave a sleepy rhythm and melody as synths add dreamy accents, a deep bass note grounds as a gentle beat brings a lulling cadence. The slowly evolving melody moves with an unhurried pace off to sleepy-land.

tracks.title: Majestic Snowy Owl
tracks.desc: And emotive clarinet leads this piece with a skyward climbing melody, resounding piano chords and a deep synth add emotive textures as millitary drums beat a serious tattoo. Uplifting and burning with nature's energy.

tracks.title: Melancholy Piano
tracks.desc: A somber piano speaks from the heart, exploring the dark with growing resolution. Silver linings peak from the corners of the sad melody, reminding that to wander is not necessarily to be lost.

tracks.title: Opening Titles and Arctic Scenes
tracks.desc: A leaping melody speaks to the wonder and beauty of nature. A sparkling opening followed by an exploring clarinet line, a piano joins the conversation with inquisitive chords.

tracks.title: Tension In The Quietness Of Nature
tracks.desc: Strings and minor notes adds an exquisite tension to this lilting piece, the languid rhythm accented by floating synth pads.

tracks.title: Touching To Bluesy Clarinet
tracks.desc: Plucked strings give a sunny edge to this glowing, building track, warm clarinet lines weave a simple, happy melody. A pause and the clarinet takes a bluesy solo, singing to the rising synth pads.

tracks.title: Be There In A Heartbeat
tracks.desc: Buzzing synths add zooming effects as a smooth beat and belled rhodes rides below, a cool spacious quality exists throughout the track as the synths slide through the stereo field.

tracks.title: Feral Destination
tracks.desc: Dynamic synth effects weave syncopated accents over a beefy kick drum, ethereal pad and angelic voices glide over the stern beat as the funky synths collide and glitch.

tracks.title: Funk Revolution
tracks.desc: Slamming snares and a hot, hot bass lead this heavy funk track, dirty wah wah guitar adds just the right feel with a smoking solo and accents.

tracks.title: Gold Standard
tracks.desc: Awesome warped and glitched bass line rumbles along with a lo-fi drum beat, claps and strings add a lightness as the wicked bass bubbles underneath.

tracks.title: Gotham Sunrise
tracks.desc: Buzzing synths work a spooky melody over an energetic step beat, smooth guitar slings ringing solos over the eager beat, a nice deep bass pegs the stepping rhythm.

tracks.title: March Of The Android
tracks.desc: Slamming machine beat lays a serious stomp, as funked out synths weave a dynamic, buzzing melody. Gurgling bass synth adds lock step notes, keeping with the robotic feel as a sweet guitar comes in with a simple but effective line.

tracks.title: Mezzaterra
tracks.desc: Cool, gliding beat with a laid back tropical feel, replete with echoing male chants, rising string hits, and groovy, ringing guitars. Wark keys, handclaps and percussion keep the groove loose.

tracks.title: Ode To A Gangsta
tracks.desc: Syncopated synth lines, deep bass and effectsed drums weave a hitched rhythm with dark tones and a shadowy demeanor. The cool beat hits a smokey break, then keeps on funkin'.

tracks.title: Oriental Transcendence
tracks.desc: Handclaps and a big kick weave a syncopated rhythm with an urgent edge, fat synth leads accent the tense feel with a dark melody. Synth effects add pulsing accents as deep burning bass holds down the punchy kicks.

tracks.title: Time Traveling
tracks.desc: Big rolly-polly bass and stuttering kicks work a dark, introverted beat, keyed synths weave a dreamy melody. Skipping hi-hat keeps the tension as the big bass slithers across the pushing beats.

tracks.title: Eternal Effervescence
tracks.desc: Sparkling, belled synths and glitch effects weave a humid and warm atmosphere, a funky kick fades in and out, working an eager beat. A sultry feeling track with cool tension.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Heavenly Prowl
tracks.desc: Warm, fat bass works a moody line, as portamento synths weave a wicked melody, drums kick in with a driving beat and break-down. Moody car driving music accented by DJ scratching and belled synth pads.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Juggernaut
tracks.desc: Glitched percussion and a big, buzzing synth bass weave a slamming dance beat, warm pads add big, bright leads. The beat kicks in and out accenting the bouncy dance feel.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Monkey Wrench
tracks.desc: Rocking, fuzzed up bass line leads this bass and drum stomp. Hypnotic, driving beats clash as computer beeping synths go crazy. A robotic break down pauses the madness, the beat builds back up to an intense groove.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Poetic Justice
tracks.desc: Moody synths and warpped disco beats lead this slamming track, a simple synth line brings the melody together as the hypnotic beat slams into a new-jack groove.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Summer Flight
tracks.desc: Organic, belled synths and finger piano weave a sparkling and calm melody as drum machine builds a worldly beat. A spacy break-down as the melody falls apart, the beat kicks back in as the warm synths rev back up. A floating, warm track with world element
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Wayward Struggle
tracks.desc: Amazing synths sound like electronic ocean waves, a glitched out beat comes in as crazy synths weave noises and effects, a pause and the beat kicks back in with amazing effects swirling around the stereo field. Utterly amazing sounds.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: C est La Vie
tracks.desc: Atmospheric pads and a stuttering kick weave a humid atmosphere accented by the stop-start patterns of the kick, sampled strings add chiming, echoing notes. The beat kicks in with a subtle drive as the pads echo and ebb.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Distortion Of Slumber
tracks.desc: Alien beeps and fuzzy percussion set a sedate pace for this evolving track, odd noises sputter and sound with syncopated rhythms growing into an off-kilter beat. A fragment of a woman's voice adds an intriguing accent to the dream-like piece.

tracks.title: Green And Metal Thumbs
tracks.desc: Warm, belled Rhodes and clockwork percussion meld into a lo-fi groove, moving with an organic pace, simple chords weave an otherworldly tune.

tracks.title: Internal Rummaging
tracks.desc: Fuzzy organ weaves a simmering sound-field, a lo-fi kick percolates in the background. Sounding somewhere between synthetic rain and a Geiger counter, the strange noises ebb and flow as the quirky percussion spells out a subterranean beat.

tracks.title: Moments Of Materiality
tracks.desc: Dusty percussion weaves an odd, organic rhythm as belled keys play a happy little riff. The rhythm fades in and out, accenting the Rhodes light-hearted riffing.

tracks.title: Moving Without Moving
tracks.desc: The synth percussion builds an easy beat with a fuzzy kick and strange percussion, the belled synths weave a ringing melody that flows in and around the lo-fi beats.

tracks.title: Pop And Hush
tracks.desc: Finger snaps add a human-like touch to this piece, building a rhythm with glitched rhythmic noises. Ringing chords build a repetitive melody that inverts and warbles with the glitched rhythm.

tracks.title: Room To Room
tracks.desc: Sputtering beats weave a quirky rhythm as strange chords flash, odd voice fragments add syncopated accents. The piece wanders and rolls untill a hand-clap comes in and the groove comes together.

tracks.title: Sitting On A Train
tracks.desc: Resounding chords echo and sweep through the stereo field, skittering synth percussion comes in as the keys warble and flow.

tracks.title: Travelogue Of A Noise To Signal Ratio
tracks.desc: Bassy kicks weave a heart beat rhythm as sampled voices stutter on beat, hand-claps bring the groove as Rhodes chords weave a subtle melody.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Concerto 5 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: A robust and resounding work, quickly building to epic proportions, moving from tense intro to triumph with the orchestra at full bore.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Concerto 5 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: With  warm and gentle strings this movement flows with a splendid calmness and generosity, the absolutely amazing piano lines move with otherworldly grace, full of charm and golden emotion.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Concerto 5 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Resounding piano plays with intense and masterful style, moving across the keys with dignity and assurance, the orchestra lifts the piano and they both soar.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 8 (Pathetique 1st movement)
tracks.desc: A rather introspective piece, moving through intense emotions from troubled to temperate. The piano lines are truly amazing, straight from the heart.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 8 (Pathetique 2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Languid lines weave an introspective melody, with a measured pace the gentle melody shines with meditative grace.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 8 (Pathetique 3rd movement)
tracks.desc: The final movement brings a lighter mood, with graceful piano lines moving with excited and powerful elegance.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 9 (Opus 14 1st movement)
tracks.desc: A lighthearted and effervescent movement, the piano played with verve and joy.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 9 (Opus 14 2nd movement)
tracks.desc: A wistful melody leads this gentle movement, the deliberate pace and thoughtful playing speak to a quest for inner peace.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 9 (Opus 14 3rd movement)
tracks.desc: The pace picks up for this masterful ending, lovely trills and explorations make the melody shine with a resounding joy.

tracks.title: Bizet Angus Dei
tracks.desc: A dark, moody piece, with  a soaring male lead, building with a sorrowful vocal to operatic heights.

tracks.title: Bizet Church Bells
tracks.desc: A warm and flowing piece that starts with a happy rhythm, turns to a string led ethereal section that harmoniously winds it way to a triumphal ending

tracks.title: Boccherini Minuet (Equal Temperament tuning)
tracks.desc: This delightful tune sings with a sweet and innocent elegance, a charming waltz that will lift the darkest spirits.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 14 (Moonlight Sonata 1st movement)
tracks.desc: This well known piano sonata begins with a ruminative movement, mournful and dramatic.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 14 (Moonlight Sonata 2nd movement)
tracks.desc: With a lighter step the second piece builds on a happy melody and explores it's rich, fertile modes, charmed and succinct.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 14 (Moonlight Sonata 3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Moving with a rapid pace, amazing piano lines flow with hypnotizing fervor, troubled, hurried and exciting.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 21 (Waldstein 1st movement)
tracks.desc: Starts minimalistic and spacial, with a gradual crescendo into fierce, virtuosic modulations.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 21 (Waldstein 2nd and 3rd movements)
tracks.desc: Sweet and pensive introductory material fades into a playful, varied adventure.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 23 (Appassionata 1st movement)
tracks.desc: Many pronounced, sweeping arpeggios color this sharply dynamic exercise of themes. Furious at times and wandering lost at others.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 23 (Appassionata 2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Graceful and simplistic, this mild-tempered movement is serene and inspiring. Magnificent arpeggios color the quiet elegance.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 23 (Appassionata 3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Powerful and hard-hitting from the start, littered with diminished harmonies that create wonderful tension ultimately leading to a climactic release.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 25 (Opus 79 2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Mostly single-paced and subtle, with lush harmonies perfect for reflection.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 25 (Opus 79 1st movement)
tracks.desc: Charging, sweeping movement with consistant tempo swings, though the theme is triumphant.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 25 (Opus 79 3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Bouncy, playful movement comprises the piece. The memorable, joyous theme is repeated often.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 26 (Les Adieux 1st movement)
tracks.desc: Short, simple motifs often with extravagent elaborations. Sweeping dynamic range.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 26 (Les Adieux 2nd movement)
tracks.desc: This sad and moving piece still allows for a glimmer of hope and in the falling chromaticisms and E-flat harmonies

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 26 (Les Adieux 3rd movement)
tracks.desc: The final movement brings light and hope with resounding chords and masterful ornamentation. Shades of anticipation echo in the warm chording and energetic, rousing tempo.

tracks.title: Black Ice
tracks.desc: Tinkling, icy piano notes descend into throbbing strings that weave a delicate melody, echoing timpani creates a dark atmosphere crescending into a final climax as the tune fades

tracks.title: Departure Of The Geese
tracks.desc: Deep, threatening bass strings weave a dark throb as sparkling woodwind notes tumble, an english horn solo brings a cheerful melody that turns into a playful exchange with plucked strings and xylophone. The piece becomes busy with lighthearted glee.

tracks.title: Floating In The Air
tracks.desc: Rising string lines and flute are accented by crisp percussion, a clarinet brings a sublime solo as the piece turns and glides along the piano notes. A smooth, engrossing piece with an open outlook.

tracks.title: Flying Away
tracks.desc: Harp and piano weave a humid atmosphere for an exotic clarinet solo, floating as if on the breeze, the charming tune winds and dances with elegant ease.

tracks.title: Full Moon
tracks.desc: Hyper pizzicato strings tinkling piano and bassy strings weave an enigmatic atmosphere. Horns, winds and percussion add flowing accents.

tracks.title: Grand Opening And Lullaby
tracks.desc: A rich and rising atmosphere of floating strings and twinkling piano weave a melodic haze for a lovely clarinet solo, upbeat and engaging the clarinet sings a simple and charming song.

tracks.title: Happy Games
tracks.desc: Sparkling percussion and tooting flutes rise like a summer sun, harp and piano join with tumbling lines, the harp brings a lead melody with a warm and sunny outlook. A clarinet solo comes in with a joyous temperament as a xylophone joins the fun.

tracks.title: The Moose Lullaby
tracks.desc: Rich floating strings weave a sumptuous atmosphere, plucked strings add a delicate rhythm as a mellow and sweet clarinet weaves a lighthearted melody over the top, the tune changes into a humorous waltz as the instruments dance with a slow, gleeful pace.

tracks.title: Sorrowful
tracks.desc: Melancholy piano and strings weave a delicate and sad melody. Floating like a memory a gentle oboe melody speaks of a sad and lonely wandering. In an dramatic conversation, bassoon and pizzicato strings play a tone game.

tracks.title: Storm And Finale
tracks.desc: Trembling strings and dark bass strings weave an encroaching and threatening melody, flute trills and piano lines tumble like raindrops, the tune shifts to a playful jazzy piece with a mysterious vibe.

tracks.title: Ancient Wonders
tracks.desc: A floating, atmospheric piece with a world music feel. Heavenly pads fade and shimmer as an ethnic flute plays bird-call sounds over a downtempo beat.

tracks.title: Bryce Canyon
tracks.desc: Distant bubbling arpeggios and hi-hat weave a ethreal rhythm as sparkling synth pads float across the stereo field.

tracks.title: Future Visions
tracks.desc: Chiming, delayed synths weave a sparkling melody, easy percussion adds a moody pulse, warm pads add a spacious atmosphere.

tracks.title: High Riser
tracks.desc: Shortwave synths swirl as a a dark bass pulse burns underneath, machine drums add a torpid rhythm. With a deadline feel.

tracks.title: Larger Than Life
tracks.desc: An easy stepping machine beat with glitchy accents moves under a humid atmosphere of synth pads, arpeggio bass lines and synth organ add smooth elements. A fluid piano line and acoustic guitar provides a warm lead melody.

tracks.title: Onwards And Upwards
tracks.desc: Subtle, soulful beat rides a deep bass line, sparkling synths add syncopated lead lines, floating and warm.

tracks.title: Skys The Limit
tracks.desc: Bubbling arpeggio and twinkling synths weave a stereophonic, spatal groove. Deep bass adds rich tones, walking piano lines create a cool melody.

tracks.title: So Into You
tracks.desc: Driving synth drums and deep bass weave a sumptious beat, after a filtered break the beat comes back in with a crystaline push. Warm, echoing synth organ adds spatal depth and a rich melody.

tracks.title: Street Smart
tracks.desc: Funky, glitched beat tumbles and churns, bass sample works a decending line, 80 style rap synth adds a dark accent. Dark booming sounds and synth effects weave a dark, syncopated melody.

tracks.title: Up And Over
tracks.desc: Bird sounds, skittering snares and warbling bass weave an atmospheric beat as synth pads swirl through the stereo field, easy gliding feeling is enhanced by the smooth synth sounds.

tracks.title: Distant Waters
tracks.desc: Resonating bell synths and raw, but elegant strings weave winding, melodramatic melodies. Ringing synth sounds give a bit of tempo to the humid, atmospheric haze.

tracks.title: Indian Lullaby
tracks.desc: Lovely ethreal synth and echoing flute weave a floating magical landscape.

tracks.title: Magic Hotel
tracks.desc: Eerie strings and tinking bells weave a dark, brooding soundscape as a lonely clarinet and harpischord add dramatic leads.

tracks.title: Middle East Rave
tracks.desc: Ethnic strings and dulcimer weave an exotic melody as hand drums beat a driving rhythm.

tracks.title: Peace Child
tracks.desc: Loving piano lines weave a gentle theme, rising synth strings add a sunny glow, gently building and overflowing with warmth.

tracks.title: Planetary Motion
tracks.desc: Piano and synth pads weave a harmonious atmosphere for strident string lines and subtle percussion, delicate yet forceful.

tracks.title: Risky Adventure
tracks.desc: Dramatic strings weave a troubled melody ad thundering percussion hightens the urgent feel, proud horns add glowing accents.

tracks.title: Thrill Of The Moment
tracks.desc: Lonely piano line rides below a driving drum beat, synth sounds build dramatic cresendos as the beat ruptures, delayed synth guitar adds dramatic accents.

tracks.title: Unexpected Romance
tracks.desc: Dark bass strings weave a spooky framework for lonesome winds and strings. With a touch of sadness and foreboding fear.

tracks.title: Victory At Last
tracks.desc: Rising, building strings weave a heady, warming atmosphere, winds and horns join escalating the growing tones, with a new beginning feel.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 30 (Opus 109 1st movement)
tracks.desc: Graceful and eloquent piano lines played with consummate vigor, flowery trills and sunny ornamentation lend a upbeat outlook to this engrossing first movement.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 30 (Opus 109 2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Melodically,a mixture of peacefulness and total drama...almost like two people speaking, one calm and one full of emotions that need expression.This feeling comes into play by the composers shift in rhythm swaying back and forth in and out of the mood.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 30 (Opus 109 3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Staying with the same general feeling as the other two movements,this movement continues the feeling and ends with a more radical incline. It is trying to end the story on a very dramatic note.

tracks.title: Accidental Nomads
tracks.desc: A lo-fi beat comprised of found sounds lays a steady, downtempo beat, sparce organ notes build a sublime melody, odd vocal noises and glitches provide ear catching accents.

tracks.title: Cassettes Of Yesteryear Today
tracks.desc: A warped found sound beat like an energetic heart pulses as rhodes tones weave a monotone melody, tapping and room sounds add a delicately organic feel to the pulsing beats.

tracks.title: Cornerside Materials
tracks.desc: Effected rhodes piano notes stutter and echo as a fuzzy kick lays a heartbeat beat. Like a transmission from another planet the song wavers and ebbs, uncontrolled and meandering.

tracks.title: Edits For The End
tracks.desc: Warbling rhodes tones build as rustling sounds peak through the background, surreal and almost ghostlike.

tracks.title: Geometry Of Escapism
tracks.desc: Drum machine adds a differnt sound, glitched and effected the beat slowly fleshes out, vocal cut up provide a rhythmic counterpiont to the crunchy beats. Mellow rhodes adds a simple melody.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata Number 1 (Opus 2 1st movement)
tracks.desc: Exciting Piano piece with dynamic scale changes. Subtle at times, but for the most part is quite moving. The piano notes move along the scales and create an uplifting feeling.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata Number 1 (Opus 2 2nd movement)
tracks.desc: This song creates a feeling of mixed emotions simultaneously . There is a calm yet uneasy feeling in the atmosphere, throughout the song.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata Number 1 (Opus 2 3rd movement)
tracks.desc: A sequence of piano notes, low and high that keep on with the same idea .  Dynamically, building up a bit, getting to a high point then reverting back to the low point.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata Number 1 (Opus 2 4th movement)
tracks.desc: Very moving piano piece. The melody speaks about all the little things in life that add up and form a big joyous picture.

tracks.title: In Between The Walls
tracks.desc: Stutter-step beats and a echoing organ weave a spaced-out lo-fi dub, effected water drop sounds wiggle and squirm as soft pads add spatal atmospheres.

tracks.title: Paper Fields Dub
tracks.desc: Echoing noises and sounds give a laid-back dub feel to this atmospheric track, a subtle bass beat give a head-nodding rhythm.

tracks.title: Proximity Of Objects
tracks.desc: A glitched beat and fuzzy static noises build a smooth, relaxed beat, ringing rhodes notes weave a warm, repeating melody.

tracks.title: Rounded Shards Of Sleet And Hail
tracks.desc: A rhythm slowly builds, like a subterranean heartbeat, as strange static noises scramble across the stereo field.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 17 (Tempest 1st movement)
tracks.desc: Alternating between calm and furious, the first movement rings with dynamic action and lulling pauses. The ascending piano lines explode into storms of ornamentation.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 17 (Tempest 2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Moving with a more somber pace, the second piece mimics the first movement with it's ornamented arpeggios and serious demeanor.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 17 (Tempest 3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Rooted in D Minor, this movement brings a brighter outlook and lighter melodies, reaching an intense climax then wandering through many key changes and emotive progressions.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 27 (Opus 90 1st movement)
tracks.desc: Complex and capricious this first movement compares the dialogue of the head with the song of the heart, moving from technical fireworks to soaring melodies.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 27 (Opus 90 2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Dynamic rhythm gives this final movement a leaping, galvanizing momentum, elegantly bounding through glorious ornament and exposition with virtuosic wit and grace.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 29 (Hammerclavier 1st movement)
tracks.desc: This intrepid and robust movement moves with a thrilling pace leaping and bounding with a joyous and galvanizing air. One of Beethoven's most challenging works, the virtuosic playing is astounding.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 29 (Hammerclavier 2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Jovial exploration in this brief 2nd movement winds it's way to a dark place then escapes, coming back to the main theme before drifting off.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 29 (Hammerclavier 3rd movement)
tracks.desc: This long movement is one of Beethoven's most dramatic, the slow and mournful tones describe a deep and endless sorrow.

tracks.title: Beethoven Piano Sonata 29 (Hammerclavier 4th movement)
tracks.desc: Timidly building with fugue-like elements, the final movement ascends to an intense and lengthy climax. Most certainly Beethoven at his finest.

tracks.title: Amends In Vain
tracks.desc: This piece builds up to  sweep us into the plot as an upbeat drum line pushes melodic strings and electric guitar forward, crashing cymbals add rhythmic accents enhancing the sweeping feel.  Horns and piano support and highlight the melody.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Blood Begets Blood
tracks.desc: A looped bass line, followed by synth sounds of a high pitched female vocal, creating a spiritual feeling.Strings and horns adding harmony. A guitar riff then follows representing the task at hand. A melodic horn visits, giving a classic approach
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Gallop Through The Sands
tracks.desc: A marching beat rhythm and an upright bass play a simple line. Horns add harmonics to the bass line. The middle bridge brings evolving dynamic changes as the strings play rhythm and harmony, a xylophone joins, then brings us back to the original verse.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Glory Underway
tracks.desc: This piece has many classic music elements. This is reflected in the march style lead by the drum and bass, accompanied by the classic instruments surrounding it. Strings creating the floor with horns on top,. Creates a  victorious feeling.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: On Another Episode
tracks.desc: Creates a thrilling action scene feeling, with percussion, accented by cymbals and bass .A male church choir accompanied by male whispers is prominent. Strings and horns take turns leading in the background . A Synth loop visits
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Out Of Time
tracks.desc: Slow and quiet classical piece. Piano and flute leading into a feeling of loss and memorial. The middle of the piece is lead by a march drum beat, creating the feeling of uprising from the fall.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Reeling Of The Reefs
tracks.desc: Strings, Bells and piano,bring warmth and a sense of hope. A military snare and xylophone in the background, playing a march beat, bring the soldiers back home.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Soldiers And Pilgrims
tracks.desc: Horns dominate this piece. A feeling of loss of good men who served their country right. A flute adds to this mood. Use of bells and a xylophone enhance the important accents by the Timpani and cymbals.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Bach Air On A G String
tracks.desc: This memorable melody flows with a grand and elegant pace, evoking enchanting visions of serenity and ease. The gentle string lines seem to sing straight from the heart.

tracks.title: Yarn Of The Buccaneer
tracks.desc: Irish sounding piece. Builds up gradually with strings, then horns and flute, to form a great victorious moment. A Xylophone and strings play a loop in the background  as  enhancers.
tracks.comp: David Flavin, ASCAP (50%), Roland Rudzitis, ASCAP  (50%)

tracks.title: Bach Badinerie
tracks.desc: The lead flute dances a merry jig, with a folksy feel this leaping piece brims with an eager and confident joy.

tracks.title: Bach Christmas Oratorio (sinfonia)
tracks.desc: An elegant and voluptuous string melody leads this seasonal track. Delightfully warm and embracing, this flowing work evokes loving scenes of holiday cheer and joy.

tracks.title: Bach Giselle (Entrance of Giselle)
tracks.desc: This delightful waltz turns and dances with a light, graceful step. The reflective, loving string lines certainly announce the entry of a beautiful character

tracks.title: Bach Miserere Mei
tracks.desc: This poignant opera echos with a heavy heart and dramatic vocal swells, the lovely voices ring out, shattering darkness in prayer and hope.

tracks.title: Bach Sheep May Safely Graze
tracks.desc: This charming work has a languid, folksy country air, rarefied and sweet. It's gentle rhythm and swelling strings evokes scenes of lush countryside and fertile fields.

tracks.title: Bach Toccata And Fugue in Dminor
tracks.desc: This spooky and well known track will put a chill up your spine with it's harrowing cathedral organ,

tracks.title: Bittersweet Dreams
tracks.desc: Rock Ballad with very deep emotions. Reflected by Electric guitar leading, accompanied by an acoustic guitar.

tracks.title: Dance In The Moonlight
tracks.desc: This waltzy and calm piece, sounds like a lullaby, yet not sleepy enough.Wants to rejoice and then will finally find rest. Performed by electric guitars. Classic stye in the composition.

tracks.title: Do Not Look Back
tracks.desc: This piece has a build that is unexpected. starts out full of action. Shifting from heavy metal guitar to a spanish guitar , then to a classic rock style. The feeling is of running away to start a new life without looking behind.

tracks.title: Fight Or Flight
tracks.desc: Fast guitars and drums, resembling a speedy train, that will not stop at its stops.

tracks.title: Home For The Holidays
tracks.desc: A Classic rock style song. Lead and accompanied by acoustic guitars. Percussion enhancing a happy, joyous, and relaxed feeling of the family home for the holidays.

tracks.title: Smooth Entrance
tracks.desc: A short, big band piece. Lead by a jazz bass and drum line. Guitars playing a  sequence of happy notes, creating a smooth jingle

tracks.title: Taking The Lead
tracks.desc: Starts out as a happy and upbeat piece. Guitars wailing, and drums rocking the house. Turns urgent towards the end, with a heavier style in the drum beat, and the guitars forming a loop, joining that feeling.

tracks.title: The Break Of Dawn
tracks.desc: A new beginning. Morning is here. Acoustic Guitar taking the lead, visited by an electric guitar with a church organ/bagpipe effect. A peaceful morning song, you can wake up to. Finally, like an alarm clock, the electric guitars signal the dawn.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 1 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Beethoven begins this Symphony with a slightly humorous air, as the opening is in Fmajor- not the more likely Cmajor- perhaps commenting on the strict rules of classical music, as slow introduction brings melodic poetry that builds to climactic heights.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 1 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: With strings leading this subdued section, gracefully ornamented the melody rises and sings with an austere pace.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 1 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: The piece begins triumphantly and fast paced. Rising winds and strings climax and pause from sublime to full-bore.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 1 (4th movement)
tracks.desc: Driving strings and winds lead this final movement , graceful building and moving forward with resounding certitude the dynamic 1st symphony reaches an emotional and climatic end.

tracks.title: Acoustic Grit
tracks.desc: Nice Acoustic piece. Dominant acoustic guitar. Electric guitar accompanies, as the bass and drums play their part . Strings in the background adding a fullness to the song and an electric piano is prominent. Starts out with a soft feel and becomes energet

tracks.title: Chill Zone
tracks.desc: A nice balance of a drum loop with Pianos and bass as the main giving an acoustic and relaxed jazzy feel.  Spanish guitar with strings in the background. Nice use of panning in the effects that visit from time to time.

tracks.title: Come On Get Up
tracks.desc: Starts out quiet and acoustic. A guitar playing an arpeggio, accompanied by a piano. Electric guitar with a distorted effect is ready to rock the house. Walking bass adds a fullness to the song. Rock drum beat makes it all happen.

tracks.title: Lift Me Higher
tracks.desc: Guitars and piano with a medium drum beat create an ambitious and spiritual feeling. The words aren't said rather felt, requesting assistance in all  endeavors and goals that we know we could achieve.

tracks.title: Slow It Down
tracks.desc: Very laid back acoustic piece. Life is going too fast. We need to take a break from working hard and take some downtime. towards the end the strings play in uplifting style, and create the feeling that now once we are relaxed we can move on.

tracks.title: Staying In The Dark
tracks.desc: Piano playing a sequence of notes, allowing the song to be built over that basic line. The bass drum loop up front and the percussion laid back somewhere in the middle. An R&B; feel with the strings visiting in and out. Guitar loops enhancing that feeling.

tracks.title: Summer Life
tracks.desc: Summer by the beach is nice, wishing we can stay forever. Accents by the  cymbals. Starts out quiet and acoustic with guitars and a basic bass line with a laid back drum beat, becomes happier in dynamics as time moves along. That is life on the beach.

tracks.title: The Acoustic Flow
tracks.desc: Guitars starting unplugged, getting the drums involved, in a natural acoustic song manner. Piano and electric guitars come to greet us happily, as the song moves along. Strings in the background adding harmony.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 2 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: A sprightly and refreshing movement, bursting strings and horns dance like the wind of a spring storm- renewing the earth with a cleansing rush.

tracks.title: Abandoned Infirmary
tracks.desc: Horror film eeriness. Bone-chilling synth sets the mood with wicked drums and bass behind, the cold  synth lines enhance the anticipation and fear.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 2 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: A warm and romantic movement that sways with a loving touch, stately strings and golden-hued horns weave a magical and dynamic melody.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 2 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Grand and bounding dynamics from the strings and winds flavor this piece, the triumphant horns speak with unfettered directness, as the strings add merry accompaniments.

tracks.title: Black Chopper
tracks.desc: An aggressive synth lays waste to the track with pounding drums keeping rhythm to an adrenaline pumping rush, accenting the rock beat with techno flavored rage.

tracks.title: Human Bondage
tracks.desc: An epic synth flow corresponds and reverberates a metal twang setting the rhythm, giving an intense mix of power and machine.

tracks.title: Idle Hands
tracks.desc: Heavy drums flowing under a dark synth mix to create an evil sound, slow and thick with a slowly fastening pace from start to finish.

tracks.title: Maelstrom Of War
tracks.desc: Quick drums set the fast pace covered by edgy synths creating a rushed and crazed feel.

tracks.title: Resentment
tracks.desc: Ghostly synths set the tone for a skin crawling sound, speeding up into a full haunted feel.

tracks.title: Seeking The Hell Hound
tracks.desc: This aggressive intro throws an attitude like a Phoenix rising from the ashes, pounding drums and sharp synths push the track forward.

tracks.title: Space Abomination
tracks.desc: Tense atmosphere swirling with a building anxiety set by subtle synth, leading you delve deeper and deeper into a realm of seclusion and secrecy.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 2 (4th movement)
tracks.desc: A bombastic beginning featuring the orchestra at full bore, the tight and erupting ornamentation scaling heights and sweeping lows. This rambunctious closing shows Beethoven at his most engaged and joyful best.

tracks.title: Twisted Metal
tracks.desc: Fast paced synth chases the drum rhythm creating an edgy, tense, and dangerous mix of speed and tension.

tracks.title: Cottage Fever
tracks.desc: Quick banjo strokes combined with rhythmic drums set a laid-back mood , smooth guitar and a casual harmonica mix in to add to the relaxing sounds.

tracks.title: Lonely Kelly Blues
tracks.desc: Slow guitar and soft drums set the rhythm while a sharp banjo warms the track, creating a homemade feeling with friends and family.

tracks.title: Mountain Frailin
tracks.desc: Sharp plucks of the banjo create a rhythmic sound giving a scenic impression of a long country road on a warm sunny day.

tracks.title: Pedal With My Steel
tracks.desc: Mellow guitar strings with soft strokes of a banjo mix a warm hearty down home feeling.

tracks.title: Prairie Flower
tracks.desc: Slow graceful guitar strings add to the steady slow rhythm crossed with an upbeat harmonica mixing to create a steady uplifting sound.

tracks.title: Salt Miner Blues
tracks.desc: Rock worthy banjo adds spice to the otherwise smooth and slow rhythm set forth by the gentle hand tapping against the wood grain of the instrument.

tracks.title: Steamboat Pickin
tracks.desc: What starts out as a ghost town gun fight quickly turns into a quick stream gushing forth with sounds of banjos and guitars mixing together before ending with twang.

tracks.title: White Mule Breakdown
tracks.desc: Friendly banjos mixed with sweet guitar strings result in a warm happy sound, crisp end of a summer day feeling.

tracks.title: The Woman I Left Behind
tracks.desc: An introductory melody consisting of rich warm feelings contained within the guitar and banjo chords and when let loose combine to create an utter beautiful small town image.

tracks.title: Family Reunion
tracks.desc: Nice happy latin beat played by drums and percussion. The guitars sweep us away,while one plays  the melody, the other plays harmony. the feeling of happiness as the guitars unify.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Last Dancers Standing
tracks.desc: Two guitars playing along in a minor scale, reflecting on hard times and times of despair.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Latin Fiddles
tracks.desc: A sequence going back and forth on a number of fiddles, accompanied by  guitars playing a combination of latin and middle eastern notes. Good action scene material.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Lost In A Dream
tracks.desc: Guitars and mandolin playing a romantic ballad. Good romantic scene.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: My Little Spanish Lady
tracks.desc: A nice latin dancing tune. Mandolin and guitars taking the lead over percussion. The feeling of a man asking his lady: Shall we dance?
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Shaking Things Up
tracks.desc: Shake it..Percussion and guitars telling us its time to start the party. Modern techno mixes with the traditional spanish guitar, to create a fun dancing tune.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Spanish Duet
tracks.desc: Layers of music, created by guitars only. A happy tune you can dance to. The feeling of reuniting after a long while.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Spanish Dusk
tracks.desc: Night has fallen, and Its off to the disco with a pure latin beat. A mixture of techno, and natural sounds of guitar, work together to create this uplifting piece of music.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 4 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: This dark and histrionic intro is sparse as a march day, the strings singing tragic lines. The orchestra comes in to blast the clouds away with thundering and heroic horns and winds, reaching skyward and encompassing it's vastness with upbeat exposition.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 4 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: The Adagio, with subtle strings contrasting the massive horn lines and commanding rhythms. The flute and violin weave tender and emotive melodies, leading the orchestra into thundering variations.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 4 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: This galloping movement sings with triumphant joy, flavored with folk dance elements, the memorable melody moves with an organic pace, brimming with dramatic power.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 4 (4th movement)
tracks.desc: Bringing the wonderful symphony to a dramatic and uproarious conclusion, the orchestra soars and moves with dramatic power and grace.

tracks.title: 3D Panic
tracks.desc: A mixture of special haunting effects created with piano strings, live violin and clarinet playing together create a 3D panic feeling. Then, with the emerging percussion loop, comes an orchestral rock piece. Good for gradually building action scenes.

tracks.title: Flurries Of Ivory And Violin Bows
tracks.desc: Piano playing a number of cascading impressionistic arpeggios along with special violin effects, creating a very uneasy feeling, leads momentarily into a tender theme on violin, with snowflakes flurrying all over the �Ivories�.

tracks.title: Flying To The Stars
tracks.desc: Nice and quiet, classical piano piece. A joyous but relaxed feeling, as we hear the fingers gliding slowly down the piano, playing some notes in allegretto, and the others at ease. The notes twinkle as the stars in the Milky Way.

tracks.title: Hymn To The Forest Goddess
tracks.desc: Deep meaning, played strings. A prayer said by someone who is deep in nature�s most magnificent spot is heard and answered by a string quintet playing an intense hymn to nature, in the style of the Habanera dance.

tracks.title: Loonlight Sonata
tracks.desc: Starts out with a nice sweeping of notes and sound effects panned to give a wind-like sweeping mysterious feeling concluded by a loon cry. A piano introduces a melody to the clarinet which grows to the heart, echoing nature�s beauty.

tracks.title: Meditative Piano
tracks.desc: Meaningful piano piece. Hidden in its name is the object of the song. Sounds as if the person is meditating and playing the notes smoothly, peacefully slipping into euphoria.

tracks.title: Powerful Gipsy Arrival
tracks.desc: Staying in the classic realm, the composer brings us a little touch of Latin. While the Latin beat is created by the bass line with piano string effects, the clarinet and violin perform a catchy melody, transporting us in a story all it�s own.

tracks.title: Reindeer Walking On Snow
tracks.desc: The image of snow falling upon a wide open space comes to mind. As the bass bells play their part, picturing the hoofs on snow, strings and the organ follow with echoing chimes. Mixing all in with a female vocal synth, to create that spiritual feel.

tracks.title: Stable And Warm Winds
tracks.desc: Picture yourself in the desert: The hypnotic synth voices, glasses and echoing clarinet assemble into a march. The ostinato harp motive with insistent snare rolls push the caravan, further and further, through the vast spaces of a desert or the arctic.

tracks.title: The Calling Of The Loon
tracks.desc: The composer steps out of the classic genre, and blowing into his cupped hands, imitates a loon calling. This leads into a short action felt bass guitar piece, concluded by a heartrending cry with clarinet harmonics, expressing nature�s plea to humanity.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 5 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Singing to struggle and turmoil, the opening piece rings a memorable melody, repeating and expounding on the theme in ever faster chromatic exposition, the strings and flute answer the grand orchestral statements with hymn-like desgns.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 5 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: This majestic piece opens with horns making sweeping gestures as a flute sings an elegant reprise. The thundering horns weave towering blasts that ring with might. It's amazing how many different feelings this movement inspires.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 5 (3rd and 4th movements)
tracks.desc: Thundering orchestra builds to great blasts of might, forever ascending to dizzying heights. Unmatched in it's dynamic and fury, this amazing piece defies explanation, on one moment slinking in the shadows and soaring skyward the next.

tracks.title: Calling Over Tension To Chopinesque
tracks.desc: Tolling bells and flowing piano lines weave a dark melody, swooning clarinet lines follow the piano. A chord change brings a reflective tone as strings add delicate accents, the clarinet and piano work together with a tone that is uncertain or world-weary

tracks.title: Contemporary Intro
tracks.desc: Strummed Piano strings and chortling clarinet weave a heady atmosphere, the bird like clarinet line tumbles and twirls till it hits a resounding low tone and the swirling atmosphere fades like a ghost.

tracks.title: Flowing Brooks
tracks.desc: Bass and percussion bring progressive accents to this flowing track, syncopated chimes and shakers drive a fertile rhythm as doubled clarinets weave an exotic melody. The contemporary feel is hi-lighted by the rhythmic interplay of the bass and percussion

tracks.title: Gypsy Retrograde Canon
tracks.desc: Military snares, struck piano strings and a descending clarinet line weave an emotive melody, the snares tense military feel is juxtaposed by outspoken clarinet and piano. Deep resounding strings give weight to the earnest rhythm and playful clarinet.

tracks.title: Life Of A Butterfly
tracks.desc: Fluttering clarinet and emotive piano weave an organic melody, deep bass notes come in and a violin sings a sad lead. The clarinet joins as a rhythm enters moving the song into a flowing progression. Warm piano and clarinet lead this dancing section.

tracks.title: Love Tango Melody
tracks.desc: Dramatic violin and clarinet weave a moody melody accented by robust piano trills. The piece moves to a blusey rag with the clarinet's smokey leads and the violin adding gypsy lines. Bass and drums bring a complex rhythm accented by tumbling piano lines.

tracks.title: Last Cry From Mother Nature
tracks.desc: Squealing clarinet and a big electric guitar weave a tortured melody, straining and groaning. A smooth drum and bass sets a steady pace as the guitar and clarinet freak out, piano and flutes add melodic accents as the slightly psychedelic track winds out.

tracks.title: Revival In Springtime
tracks.desc: Tinkling, descending piano lines signal the birth of spring, the fantastical piano melody trundles like the sound of change and growth moving with a jolly flow. Plucked and strummed piano strings create a haunting and exotic atmosphere.

tracks.title: Sonate For A Loon
tracks.desc: Treated piano strings and squawking clarinet build an emotive atmosphere, resounding hits with fluttering clarinet weave a sumptuous swooping melody like a bird on wing, changing cadence to a foxtrot and slowing to a meditative recap of the first section

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 7 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Bold orchestral strokes are accented by sweetly singing strings and winds, a rhythm slowly builds and bursts forth with a commanding and inspired exuberance.

tracks.title: Schumann Piano Concerto 1 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: Elegiac strings support the elegantly sweeping piano as this piece moves dramatically forward.  The piece moves between powerful triumphant themes and softly plaintive melodies from subtle strings and graceful piano.

tracks.title: Schumann Piano Concerto 1 (2nd and 3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Piano and strings dance forward subtly as the orchestra slowly builds.  Sweeping strings are guided by the graceful piano, leading the piece to build dramatically before reaching a triumphant conclusion.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 7 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: Moody strings set the tone for this darker movement, fluid strings sing gently, with a timid step and modest climaxes.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 7 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Leaping to life the strings begin our adventure, rising with joyful notes and quieting for subtle string exposition, slowly building, the piece erupts and quiets with delighted glee.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 7 (4th movement)
tracks.desc: This Galloping movement is full of emotion and motion. Riding high with a rollicking rhythm that pushes the throbbing horns and ringing strings ever forward, pushing to grand heroic heights.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 8 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: This fast movement looses no time in setting the stage, leaping into the main melody with fashionable aplomb. A commanding melody with gravitas and wit.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 8 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: The opening rhythm moves like a secret that can't be kept, the strings moving from quiet to loud but keeping a strident pace. There is an underlying feeling of mirth, the orchestra is in on the joke, and plays with delight.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 8 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: This elegant movement is lead by swooning strings, moving with a delicately rising pace. An engrossing and dynamic middle piece quiets to a sparkling stringed section, and rises with a call and response motif.

tracks.title: Beethoven Symphony 8 (4th movement)
tracks.desc: Flashing and grand fireworks erupt in this dynamic final movement, perhaps the most intricate by Beethoven. Both loud and harmonious, the orchestra nails the melody and decorates it with joyful aplomb.

tracks.title: Schumann Symphony 1 (1st and 2nd movements)
tracks.desc: An elegiac theme sweeps through the orchestra to open this piece powerfully.  The whole orchestra works together to turn the piece from melancholy to triumphant.

tracks.title: Schumann Symphony 1 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Lush and graceful strings move with poignant emotion as the dramatic melody glides along.

tracks.title: Schumann Symphony 1 (4th movement)
tracks.desc: A tense and dramatic theme begins this movement before a contrasting theme is introduced.  The orchestra drives forward gracefully and powerfully before the piece softly comes to a close.

tracks.title: Smetana Moldau River
tracks.desc: This piece begins subtly as woodwinds wind their way slowly out of silence before an epic melody emerges.  Powerful bursts from horns and strings drive the piece forward dramatically as tension builds steadily.

tracks.title: Best Kind Of Bliss
tracks.desc: Poppy synth sounds weave an upbeat melody as skipping snares push the pulsing melody forward. Deep bass plays a musicical line as the happy beats and synth bop along.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Busting Out
tracks.desc: Soufull bellooed synth and fat thumpin bass lead this swirling, upbeat track. The bouncy synths and pulsing beats give the feel of the world sailing by your windshield on a rainwet city street.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Ecstasy In Orbit
tracks.desc: Slamming techo beat rocks with a throbbing forward thrust, a filtered break then the beat kicks back in with a head nodding ferocity as the shining synths percolate and dance.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Final Showdown
tracks.desc: Jacked up synth noises collide with a slamming hi-hat beat, pulsing synths and dark bass weave a robotic melody as this huge, slamming kick comes in, the beat becomes hypnotic and pounding, a short break relieves the pressure, but only for a moment.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Look My Way
tracks.desc: A stuttering rhythm is accent by vocal samples and banging synth lines, the piece shifts gears and becomes more of a dance beat, the slamming clockwork snares beating a motivational beat.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Supremacy
tracks.desc: A kicking techno track with lots of energy, ripping arpeggio and crowd sounds weave an upbeat atmosphere as swirling synths wind through the stereo field, a constant kick keeps a locked in rhythm.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Throbs And Pulses
tracks.desc: Dark bass synth and a slamming step beat lead this funky track, insanely filterd synths squack and thrash, a new jack rhythm is lead by a large slamming synth line. With a percolating, motivational feel.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Twirling Androids
tracks.desc: A punchy mezmerizing beat moves with a dark drive as tumbling arpeggios slide and swerve, a dark thumping bass keeps the beat pegged as effected voices make strange noises across the stereo field.
tracks.comp: Dean Barrett, APRA (50%), Judy Whittaker, APRA (50%)

tracks.title: Brahms Symphony 4 (1st movement)
tracks.desc: A warm and enticing movement, swelling romantic melodies abound, moving with ease through shades of light and dark.

tracks.title: Brahms Symphony 4 (2nd movement)
tracks.desc: A trepidatious beginning as the melody steps lightly, winds and strings weave a halting theme, rich with the flavor of winter, deliberate solos move with a methodical rhythm but retain a delightful organic feel.

tracks.title: Brahms Symphony 4 (3rd movement)
tracks.desc: Turning the theme around and lifting it with a more firm and vigorous hand, the orchestra colors and ornaments with deft aplomb. Rising and leaping with assurance not found on the previous movements.

tracks.title: Brahms Symphony 4 (4th movement)
tracks.desc: This final movement spirals with apprehension, gradually building to weighty and obstinate crescendos. Moving at times with a dancing rhythm others with a light shining melody but always returning to the dark and troubled theme.

tracks.title: Evil Curse
tracks.desc: Deep and evil bass strings weave a slithering and dark atmosphere, slowed, effected drums keep a turgid rhythm.

tracks.title: Holy Church
tracks.desc: Haunted choral voices and a poignant triangle bell weave a somber and hopeless atmosphere, evil bass strings add a dark atmosphere.

tracks.title: Mystic Revelation
tracks.desc: A rising gothic chorus hints at a great but mysterious discovery, deep winding bass strings and rhythm accents build a foreboding background.

tracks.title: No Youth
tracks.desc: Effected, echoing drums and slithering noises build an evil atmosphere, a lonely violin sings a morbid melody and the noises echo, scrape and fade.

tracks.title: Old Monastery
tracks.desc: Dark atmospheres and unearthly vocal chorus weave a dark, and foreboding atmosphere, fading and rising like a last breath.

tracks.title: Sousa Liberty Bell
tracks.desc: A jolly melody from the horns leads the way as snares crackle and cymbals crash, evoking a triumphant mood.

tracks.title: Sousa Semper Fidelis
tracks.desc: Precise percussion drives the regal melody forward as the horns lend the piece a heroic mood.

tracks.title: Sousa Stars and Stripes Forever
tracks.desc: A driving march, this piece is epic and triumphant as the joyous melody bursts forth from powerful horns.

tracks.title: Sousa The Thunderer
tracks.desc: This march is driven forward by persistent percussion as the grand melody unfolds with graceful power.

tracks.title: Sousa Washington Post
tracks.desc: This march drives joyfully forward as the rousing melody rises and falls in intensity, all lending to the piece's triumphant feel.

tracks.title: Strauss Die Fledermaus Overture
tracks.desc: Scurrying strings and horns open the piece powerfully before a softly sweeping section takes hold and gradually builds in intensity.  Crashing percussion and urgent strings drive the piece to a powerful conclusion.

tracks.title: Strauss Die Fledermaus Czardas
tracks.desc: Emotive vocals lead this piece as lush strings provide glowing harmonic support.  Winding wind instruments and subtle percussion fill out the sound as the vocals soar with graceful power.

tracks.title: Strauss Blue Danube
tracks.desc: A softly lilting melody gracefully dances forwards as lush harmonic motion lends weight to the piece.  The piece builds momentum with the pleasant melody driving forward with subtle intensity.

tracks.title: Suppe Light Cavalry (Overture)
tracks.desc: Dramatic strings open this piece powerfully as a quietly intense melody unfolds.  The unison strings are joined by triumphant trumpets and crashing percussion as the piece picks up in intensity and drives to an epic conclusion.

tracks.title: Tchaikovsky Overture 1812 Main Theme
tracks.desc: Fluttering strings and soft horns start the piece as it builds steadily to epic heights.  Pounding percussion, furiously sweeping and powerful horns carry the regal melody to a triumphant conclusion.

tracks.title: Tchaikovsky Nutcracker Overture
tracks.desc: A playful melody emerges from lilting strings and soft woodwinds wind through the orchestra as the piece dances along gracefully.

tracks.title: Tchaikovsky Nutcracker Sugar Plum Fairy
tracks.desc: Soft pizzicato strings provide support for the mystical melody that chimes its way along gracefully.

tracks.title: Tchaikovsky Nutcracker Russian Dance
tracks.desc: Powerful strings play an exciting melody as the piece drives forward with eager excitement.

tracks.title: Tchaikovsky Nutcracker Chinese Dance
tracks.desc: A bouncing pulse forms the backdrop for the lilting melody carried by the flutes.

tracks.title: Tchaikovsky Nutcracker Waltz Of The Flowers
tracks.desc: The orchestra works with lush harmonic gestures as a lilting harp leads the way to open the piece.  Sweeping strings dance along with graceful power as the beautiful melody carries the piece forward.

tracks.title: Karachi Marketplace
